INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (343,1,'2020-11-04 02:41:28','2020-11-04 02:41:28','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For the release of their single Amsterdamned — Yellow Claw wanted to create a comic universe. With Yellow Claw’s frontmen, Jim and Nils, telling the backstory of Yellow Claw through synonymous vampire lore set in modern-day Amsterdam. The animated music video serves as a prequel to the comic book released shortly after in their own comic book store — during Amsterdam Dance Event (ADE) 2019. <span class=\"dn di-l\">Accompanied by a merchandise series faithful to any comic saga, including action figures, clothing, mugs, skateboards, to name but a few.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I designed and directed the identity of the Amsterdamned universe overseeing multiple international creative teams.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Yellow Claw <br>Amsterdamned','','publish','open','open','','yellow-claw-amsterdamned','','','2020-11-08 14:13:31','2020-11-08 14:13:31','',0,'http://tomderegt.local/?p=343',0,'post','',0);
