INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (470,1,'2020-11-05 21:53:09','2020-11-05 21:53:09','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For my collaboration with Bud, I was asked to design a beanie and a limited edition jacket. The beanie is available at each Bud stockist throughout The Netherlands as of November 9th, 2020, featuring a 3D embroidered Bud \'B\' with three additional patches and a woven label that can be applied based on personal preference. The ten varsity jackets are won only through a randomly selected raffle. <span class=\"dn db-l\">They include overlapping chenille embroidery on the front and back of the coat and leather sleeves and wool body </span>. They are numbered as well as custom embroidered with the raffle winners\' names. For the campaign images and look book, I worked closely with and collaborated with photographer Calvin Pausania.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Client: Bud</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Agency: Wink</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Role: Direction &amp; Graphic Design</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photography: Calvin Pausania</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','BUDX','','inherit','closed','closed','','242-revision-v1','','','2020-11-05 21:53:09','2020-11-05 21:53:09','',242,'http://tomderegt.local/uncategorized/242-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
