INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (501,1,'2020-11-05 22:25:42','2020-11-05 22:25:42','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For my collaboration with Bud I was asked to design a beanie and a limited edition jacket. The beanie is available at all Bud stockists throughout The Netherlands come November 9th 2020<span class=\"dn db-l\">— It features a 3D embroidered Bud ‘B’ — 3 additional patches and a woven label that can be applied to personal preference </span>. The 10 varsity jackets can be won through a raffle. <span class=\"dn db-l\">They have overlapping chenille embroidery on front and back, leather sleeves and wool body </span>. They are numbered and custom embroidered with the raffle winners names. For the campaign images and look book I collaborated with photographer Calvin Pausania.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','BudX <br>Tom de Regt','','inherit','closed','closed','','406-revision-v1','','','2020-11-05 22:25:42','2020-11-05 22:25:42','',406,'http://tomderegt.local/uncategorized/406-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (502,1,'2020-11-05 22:25:55','2020-11-05 22:25:55','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When Buutvrij for life was asked to bring hyper local .amsterdam domain extensions to the attention of every person in The Netherlands, we created a tongue and cheek campaign — in true Amsterdam dialect rarely seen in advertising. We released a nation wide out of home campaign and created 3 TVC’s featuring satiric Amsterdam archetypes. The campaign got a lot of media attention and a neighbours quarrel with Amsterdam’s rival city Rotterdam.<br>It also was awarded a National Art Directors Club Award for copywriting.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Agency: Buutvrij for Life<br>Role: Art Direction &amp; Copywriting<br>Copywriting: Ralph Edelstein</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','PuntAmsterdam <br> Geef mij maar .amsterdam','','inherit','closed','closed','','414-revision-v1','','','2020-11-05 22:25:55','2020-11-05 22:25:55','',414,'http://tomderegt.local/uncategorized/414-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (503,1,'2020-11-05 22:26:09','2020-11-05 22:26:09','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Buutvrij for Life created StedelijkX. We asked 12 interesting young individuals from Amsterdam to host an audio tour past their favourite works in Amsterdam’s Stedelijk Museum. The tours where personal and short. Made by people with a busy schedule — for people with a busy schedule.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Agency: Buutvrij for life<br>Role: Graphic Design &amp; Art Directon</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Stedelijk Museum <br> StedelijkX','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2020-11-05 22:26:09','2020-11-05 22:26:09','',419,'http://tomderegt.local/uncategorized/419-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
